---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About Us | Life-ing Together"
  description="Meet Pankhuri and Kaushal, the minds behind Life-ing Together who are always seeking new experiences and asking questions."
>
  <!-- Resource hints for faster loading -->
  <link rel="preload" href="/images/miscellaneous/about-us/about_us-800w.webp" as="image" type="image/webp" fetchpriority="high" />
  
  <!-- Critical CSS -->
  <style is:inline>
    .profile-image {
      aspect-ratio: 1/1;
      object-fit: cover;
    }
    .section-card {
      will-change: transform;
    }
    
    /* Custom hero text positioning */
    .custom-hero-text {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 30%;
      left: 50%;
      right: 0;
      text-align: center;
      z-index: 10;
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .custom-hero-text {
        bottom: 15%;
      }
    }
  </style>
  
  <!-- Custom hero section with better text positioning -->
  <section class="relative h-[70vh]">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
      <picture>
        <source 
          srcset="/images/miscellaneous/about-us/about_us-400w.webp 400w,
                  /images/miscellaneous/about-us/about_us-800w.webp 800w,
                  /images/miscellaneous/about-us/about_us.webp 1200w" 
          type="image/webp">
        <img 
          src="/images/miscellaneous/about-us/about_us.jpg"
          srcset="/images/miscellaneous/about-us/about_us.jpg 1200w"
          alt="The People Life-ing Together" 
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          width="1200"
          height="800"
          fetchpriority="high"
        />
      </picture>
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black opacity-40"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="custom-hero-text text-white px-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-4">The People Life-ing Together</h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl">A bit about our lives, curiosities, and travel philosophy</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <main class="bg-gray-50 py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <!-- Introduction Section -->
      <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-md p-8 transform hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 section-card">
          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-primary-700 text-center">Our Story</h2>
            
            <p class="mb-4">
              We're two folks who found each other and decided to navigate life's journey together. 
              While our professional lives keep us grounded in the corporate world, our shared love for 
              exploration fuels our adventures around the globe.
            </p>
            
            <p class="mb-4">
              What drives us is our insatiable curiosity and constant questioning. We love diving deep into 
              topics that interest us, whether it's local history, cultural traditions, or the best way to make 
              authentic local stories. This reflects our shared philosophy of valuing depth over breadth in 
              everything we do - we'd rather know a few things deeply than many things superficially.
            </p>
            
            <p class="mb-4">
              Our approach to travel mirrors this mindset – we believe in taking our time. Even though 
              our jobs don't allow us to spend months on end in a single country, we definitely allocate 
              more than the average time to each place we visit. This deliberate pace lets us 
              absorb the essence of each destination, form meaningful connections, and discover hidden gems 
              that most tourists never see.
            </p>
            
            <p class="mb-4">
              We both live with the interesting tension of being simultaneously ambitious and laid-back.
              Sometimes we're driven by career goals and achievements, and other times we just want to 
              take it slow and enjoy life's simple pleasures. This duality shapes our travel style as well - 
              structured enough to be meaningful, relaxed enough to be enjoyable.
            </p>
            
            <p>
              Through Life-ing Together, we share our experiences, the questions we ask, and the 
              answers we find – sometimes profound, sometimes amusing, but always authentic.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      
      <!-- Meet Us Section -->
      <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-10 text-center text-primary-700">Meet Us</h2>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <!-- Pankhuri Profile -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-md overflow-hidden transform hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 section-card">
            <div class="p-6">
              <div class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full overflow-hidden mx-auto mb-6 bg-primary-100">
                <picture>
                  <source 
                    srcset="/images/miscellaneous/about-us/pankhuri-400w.webp 400w,
                            /images/miscellaneous/about-us/pankhuri-800w.webp 800w,
                            /images/miscellaneous/about-us/pankhuri.webp"
                    type="image/webp"
                  />
                  <img 
                    src="/images/miscellaneous/about-us/pankhuri.jpg" 
                    alt="Pankhuri Maheshwari" 
                    class="profile-image w-full h-full object-cover"
                    width="128"
                    height="128"
                    loading="eager"
                    decoding="sync"
                  />
                </picture>
              </div>
              
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-center text-primary-700">Pankhuri Maheshwari</h3>
              
              <ul class="space-y-4 mb-6">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-primary-500 mr-2">✦</span>
                  <span>Chartered Accountant specializing in transfer pricing and international finance with a keen analytical mind</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-primary-500 mr-2">✦</span>
                  <span>Balances her professional intensity with a love for travel, reading, and discovering hidden local experiences</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-primary-500 mr-2">✦</span>
                  <span>Known for her ability to find the perfect balance between planned activities and spontaneous adventures</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
              
              <div class="flex justify-center space-x-4">
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/pankhuri-maheshwari-195845159/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800" aria-label="LinkedIn">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                    <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/>
                  </svg>
                </a>
                <a href="https://pankhurimaheshwari.in/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-purple-600 hover:text-purple-800" aria-label="Personal Website">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                  </svg>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Kaushal Profile -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-md overflow-hidden transform hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 section-card">
            <div class="p-6">
              <div class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full overflow-hidden mx-auto mb-6 bg-primary-100">
                <picture>
                  <source 
                    srcset="/images/miscellaneous/about-us/kaushal-400w.webp 400w,
                            /images/miscellaneous/about-us/kaushal-800w.webp 800w,
                            /images/miscellaneous/about-us/kaushal.webp"
                    type="image/webp"
                  />
                  <img 
                    src="/images/miscellaneous/about-us/kaushal.jpg" 
                    alt="Kaushal Mohan" 
                    class="profile-image w-full h-full object-cover"
                    width="128"
                    height="128"
                    loading="eager"
                    decoding="sync"
                  />
                </picture>
              </div>
              
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-center text-primary-700">Kaushal Mohan</h3>
              
              <ul class="space-y-4 mb-6">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-primary-500 mr-2">✦</span>
                  <span>Product Manager in the startup ecosystem with a passion for building innovative solutions</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-primary-500 mr-2">✦</span>
                  <span>Enthusiastic about geography, exploration, and history, often serving as our unofficial tour guide</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-primary-500 mr-2">✦</span>
                  <span>Brings an energetic yet thoughtful approach to travel, always seeking to understand the deeper context of each place</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
              
              <div class="flex justify-center space-x-4">
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/kaushal-mohan/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800" aria-label="LinkedIn">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                    <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/>
                  </svg>
                </a>
                <a href="https://www.kaushalmohan.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-purple-600 hover:text-purple-800" aria-label="Personal Website">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                  </svg>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      
      <!-- Our Travel Approach -->
      <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-md p-8 transform hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 section-card">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-center text-primary-700">Our Travel Approach</h2>
          
          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
            <p class="mb-6">
              When we travel, we try to blend in rather than stand out. We prefer local cafes over tourist traps, 
              public transportation over tour buses, and authentic experiences over Instagram hotspots.
            </p>
            
            <p class="mb-6">
              We love starting our days early, wandering through morning markets when cities are just waking up. 
              We're equally content spending hours at a local cafe, observing daily life and chatting with residents, 
              as we are visiting famous landmarks.
            </p>
            
            <p>
              Our itineraries always have room for spontaneity – some of our most memorable experiences have been 
              unplanned detours based on local recommendations. This approach has led us to hidden gems in Uzbekistan, 
              authentic family restaurants in Vietnam, and breathtaking viewpoints in Dubai that weren't in any guidebook.
              </p>
            </div>
            
          <div class="mt-10 text-center">
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-700 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg transition duration-300">
              Get in Touch With Us
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Add will-change for elements that animate */
  .section-card {
    will-change: transform;
  }
  
  /* Content visibility for below-the-fold sections */
  section:not(:first-child) {
    content-visibility: auto;
    contain-intrinsic-size: 0 500px;
  }
  
  /* Optimize rendering */
  .profile-image {
    contain: paint;
  }
</style>